title: Back to the Future DeLorean Time Machine Coming to Rocket League on October 21
text: Back to the Future DeLorean Time Machine Coming to Rocket League on October 21 03:13 PM - October 12, 2015 by Steve_OS The Back to the Future DeLorean Time Machine will make its way to Rocket League, in the Back to the Future Car Pack for $1.99, on October 21. Check out the teaser trailer here .
